  async processCommand(command, canvasContext) {
    // Include current canvas state in Strike analysis
    const enrichedCommand = {
      ...command,
      canvasState: canvasContext,
      activeShapes: canvasContext.shapes.length,
      selectedTools: canvasContext.currentTool
    };

    return this.aiPathIntelligence.processWithContext(enrichedCommand);
  }
}
```

## üìã Specific Recommendations for End-to-End Connections

### Priority 1: Canvas State Bridge
**Implement live canvas data access for Strike/AI systems**

1. **Add Canvas State IPC Handler** (chrome-container-app/src/ipc/handlers.js):
